   CUNNINGHAM-NOVEL (Undated) _ Talking to Michael Cunningham,
whose novel ``The Hours,'' an impressionistic response to Virginia
Woolf's ``Mrs. Dalloway,'' was awarded the Pulitzer Prize for
fiction. By Mel Gussow.
