   JOEMURRAY-COLUMN _ LUFKIN, Texas _ Walking the aisles of the
supermarket, humming an old song, ``If I Only Had a Match.'' Can
you imagine, being out of matches? (Murray, Cox News Service) MOVED
MONDAY.
