 &HT;    Laugh it up
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   There are hundreds of places to find e-mail humor _ just type
``jokes'' into any Internet search engine and you'll find them.
Here are a few Web sites that archive jokes or send them out daily.
Some label off-color jokes; at others, it's reader beware.
