<P>
   LIFESTYLE
</P>
<P>
   EMAIL-HUMOR _ On the Internet, everybody's a comedian _ but not
everybody's funny. Humor spam _ e-mailed jokes sent to dozens of
recipients _ amuses some and angers others. It can also embarrass,
if pulled up at work, and even bore: How many times can you read
the Smithsonian Barbie joke before you start your own top 10 list _
``Why I Hate the Forward Button''? (Lee, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). WITH ILLUSTRATION. MOVED.
