 ART ADV.: Photos with KOSOVO-MEDITATE, CHILDREN-VIOLENCE,
AUTHOR-BREASHEARS and HKN-BRUINS-DAFOE are being transmitted to NYT
Photo Service subscribers.  
 For Immediate Release  
 
