childhood darkened by a violent father to his ambivalence about the
forbidding mountain to which his name has become tightly linked. By
Nathan Cobb. (2 takes) PHOTO
</P>
<P>
   BOOK-COUNTRY (Undated) _ ``The Country Life'' is an oddly
ingratiating social comedy about an unlikely governess who finds
herself working for an impossible family. By Diane White.
</P>
