   KOSOVO-FUEL (Washington) _ Some military experts dispute NATO's
ability to easily choke off the Serb fuel supplies. By Elizabeth
Becker.
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-CONGRESS (Washington) _ The emergency request for $6
billion reopens congressional debate on Kosovo. By Tim Weiner.
