<P>
   HKN-STANLEYCUP _ Hockey fans say that there is nothing in team
sports to match the Stanley Cup playoffs for history and intensity.
The road to Lord Stanley's cup begins as the NHL playoffs open with
Detroit shooting for a third straight title. But the Red Wings will
be challenged by Dallas and Colorado in the Western Conference. The
Eastern Conference looks wide open, with no clear favorite.
(Schultz, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
