   Citrus juicer
</P>
<P>
   Roasting thermometer
</P>
<P>
   Bottle opener
</P>
<P>
   Can opener
</P>
<P>
   Set of measuring spoons: 1 tablespoon, 1 teaspoon, 1/2 teaspoon,
1/4 teaspoon
</P>
<P>
   1- and 2-cup measuring cups with pouring spout
</P>
<P>
   1- and 2-cup jars with screw-on lids
</P>
