   SPIRITUAL-DIET (Undated) _ LeAnn Larsen has fought the battle of
the bulge since she was a teenager. Over the years, she has sampled
one weight loss program after another, without much success. ``I
tried them all,'' Larsen says, ``Nutri System, Weight Watchers,
Jenny Craig, dexatrim pills.'' Now she has put her trust in God and
in a Christian weight loss program that was founded five years ago
in a Tennessee strip mall and has grown to an estimated 20,000
chapters nationwide.
