   &UR; WHO SAID WHAT &LR;
</P>
<P>
   ``Forget all those health clinics and gyms. Sex is the best cure
for everything, especially stress. If I have a good night of sex,
all my problems are gone by 10 o'clock in the morning.''
</P>
<P>
   _ Grace Jones in the Sunday Independent of London.
</P>
