<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-20 20:55 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6453 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-CLINTON-TEX     04-20 0054
</HEADER>
