<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-20 21:06 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6466 &Cx1f; tad-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-KOSOVO-STRIKES-0421-C     04-20 0804
