addressed reporters during a news conference at the White House on
Tuesday. Clinton administration officials said Monday they will use
this week's NATO summit to push for allied agreement on economic
sanctions including an oil embargo to deny Yugoslavia the ability
to wage war in Kosovo. (Justin Lane/New York Times Photo)
</P>
